1
00:00:49,330 --> 00:00:51,390
The children sent into the mountains

2
00:00:51,500 --> 00:00:53,000
never received any protection.

3
00:00:53,000 --> 00:00:55,000
All of them were killed by evil spirits.

4
00:00:55,000 --> 00:00:57,060
Thank you three for saving our lives.

5
00:00:57,120 --> 00:00:58,830
I was foolish

6
00:00:58,870 --> 00:01:00,330
and blinded by the evil spirits.

7
00:01:00,330 --> 00:01:02,120
I harmed the children of the village.

8
00:01:02,120 --> 00:01:03,120
I deserve to die a thousand deaths.

9
00:01:03,120 --> 00:01:04,290
The evil spirits have been eliminated.

10
00:01:04,290 --> 00:01:05,370
Abolish this bad custom from now on.

11
00:01:05,370 --> 00:01:07,200
Protecting the villagers is the right path.

12
00:01:07,200 --> 00:01:09,000
The resentment of the wrongfully dead children has dispersed.

13
00:01:09,000 --> 00:01:11,700
Living a good life is the best comfort to them.

14
00:01:11,910 --> 00:01:15,539
Luoxia Village thoroughly abolishes the bad custom of mountain sacrifice.

15
00:01:15,539 --> 00:01:17,000
For all generations to come,

16
00:01:17,000 --> 00:01:19,539
we will never sacrifice innocent children again.

17
00:01:19,539 --> 00:01:20,800
If this oath is broken,

18
00:01:20,830 --> 00:01:22,370
may lightning strike us dead.

19
00:01:22,370 --> 00:01:23,160
Tear it down.

20
00:01:51,000 --> 00:01:52,330
Who exactly am I?

21
00:01:52,910 --> 00:01:54,910
Why am I born as one with a shadow?

22
00:01:59,160 --> 00:02:01,540
Adeng, drink some warm water.

23
00:02:01,540 --> 00:02:04,540
You haven't eaten much since you woke up this morning.

24
00:02:09,699 --> 00:02:12,160
I'm fine, don't worry.

25
00:02:12,660 --> 00:02:14,830
Adeng, don't think too much.

26
00:02:15,330 --> 00:02:16,500
No matter who you are,

27
00:02:16,500 --> 00:02:18,500
no matter what you carried in the past,

28
00:02:18,500 --> 00:02:20,660
or whether you remember your past or not,

29
00:02:20,660 --> 00:02:21,910
I will be with you.

30
00:02:26,200 --> 00:02:28,160
Adeng, you still have me.

31
00:02:28,329 --> 00:02:29,730
We will all stay with you.

32
00:02:29,829 --> 00:02:32,360
We will definitely find the answers you want.

33
00:02:45,120 --> 00:02:46,180
General Dingyuan.

34
00:02:46,329 --> 00:02:47,410
Lady Dudeng.

35
00:02:47,660 --> 00:02:50,950
I am waiting for you here by His Majesty's order.

36
00:02:51,290 --> 00:02:54,120
His Majesty heard that you can bridge Yin and Yang and guide the dead souls.

37
00:02:54,120 --> 00:02:55,660
He has an important matter to ask of you.

38
00:02:55,660 --> 00:02:58,660
Please enter the palace immediately for an audience.

39
00:02:59,120 --> 00:03:00,330
His Majesty summoned us so suddenly.

40
00:03:00,330 --> 00:03:01,830
Is there a specific decree?

41
00:03:01,830 --> 00:03:03,160
Adeng just finished eliminating evil spirits.

42
00:03:03,160 --> 00:03:04,200
She suffered internal injuries.

43
00:03:04,200 --> 00:03:06,200
I'm afraid she can't bear the complicated etiquette in the palace.

44
00:03:06,200 --> 00:03:07,700
If it's not a matter of great importance,

45
00:03:07,700 --> 00:03:10,160
please allow her to rest for a few days first.

46
00:03:12,330 --> 00:03:13,390
It doesn't matter.

47
00:03:13,750 --> 00:03:14,950
His Majesty summons us,

48
00:03:14,950 --> 00:03:16,200
we cannot decline.

49
00:03:16,410 --> 00:03:20,329
Besides, I also want to see what His Majesty's important matter

50
00:03:21,410 --> 00:03:22,540
exactly is.

51
00:03:23,410 --> 00:03:24,620
I will go too.

52
00:03:24,620 --> 00:03:26,870
I can take care of Adeng's health at any time.

53
00:03:26,870 --> 00:03:28,200
If anyone makes things difficult in the palace,

54
00:03:28,200 --> 00:03:29,700
we can look out for each other.

55
00:03:29,700 --> 00:03:31,579
It's fine for you to go along, miss.

56
00:03:31,579 --> 00:03:33,329
But the rules in the palace are strict.

57
00:03:33,329 --> 00:03:35,329
Please speak and act cautiously.

58
00:03:35,370 --> 00:03:36,790
Do not wander around

59
00:03:37,000 --> 00:03:38,860
or discuss politics recklessly.

60
00:04:02,830 --> 00:04:06,700
Your Majesty, Lady Dudeng's spirit lamp can not only bridge Yin and Yang,

61
00:04:06,700 --> 00:04:08,700
but also help you gain immortality.

62
00:04:08,750 --> 00:04:09,910
You have been on the throne for many years,

63
00:04:09,910 --> 00:04:10,950
working hard on state affairs.

64
00:04:10,950 --> 00:04:12,620
If you can get the spirit lamp,

65
00:04:12,620 --> 00:04:14,120
you can rule the empire forever

66
00:04:14,120 --> 00:04:16,370
and avoid the suffering of aging, sickness, and death.

67
00:04:16,370 --> 00:04:17,660
Why not do it?

68
00:04:20,579 --> 00:04:21,950
You are right.

69
00:04:22,540 --> 00:04:24,160
Never age, never die.

70
00:04:24,750 --> 00:04:26,870
Control the spirit lamp and bridge Yin and Yang.

71
00:04:26,870 --> 00:04:28,500
If I can get the spirit lamp,

72
00:04:29,000 --> 00:04:31,000
I can live forever

73
00:04:31,160 --> 00:04:32,760
and rule the empire forever.

74
00:04:32,909 --> 00:04:34,950
Keep a close eye on their every move.

75
00:04:35,750 --> 00:04:38,330
You must get that bronze spirit lamp.

76
00:04:38,620 --> 00:04:40,080
There must be no mistakes.

77
00:04:43,000 --> 00:04:44,060
Yes, Your Majesty.

78
00:04:54,000 --> 00:04:56,000
Since they have come to the capital,

79
00:04:56,080 --> 00:04:58,120
they shouldn't expect to retreat unscathed.
